Title: Elemental Hors D'Oeuvres
Description:
The cloudrooks cannot possibly circle forever, and I cannot bear more of them being lost. But maybe they'd roost if we tempted them with their favorite food?

The eels that swim in these waters carry a small electrical charge not unlike the mosswool favored by their faster, stronger cousins the stormrooks. I once reasoned that cloudrooks might enjoy the eels for similar reasons. 

And I confess... I've been feeding them the eels ever since. 

Gather some up and give it a go.
CompletionText: The eels may not pack quite the punch of Rambleshire mosswool, but the cloudrooks seem to prefer it that way.
RewardText:
These should do.

Hope you didn't get any nasty shocks gathering them up.

We can restore some energy to the cloudrooks and show them that it's safe to land.
